<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="description" content="Tum Guessr is a guessing game, in which you are somewhere on a TUM campus, you'll be shown a picture and need to find out where you are.">
    <title>TUM Guessr</title>
	  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">	
	  <script src="/js/tracking.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body style="overflow: auto; padding-bottom: 5rem">
    {{> header}}
		<div class="content">
			<h1>Welcome to TUM Guessr</h1>
			<div class="wip" style="width: 70%; margin: 0 auto">
        <p>
          Choose a campus below to start a game. Create an account or login for Uploading your own pictures and more!
        </p>
        <p>
          Each round of a game you will be shown a random picture from somewhere on the campus.
          Your goal is to guess the location the picture was taken in.
          You can pan around and zoom in to find details that might help you find the location and then select it on the map.
          The closer you get, the more points you'll earn. Good luck!
        </p>
      </div>
			<div class="carousel" id="carousel">
				<div class="card" data-name="muenchen">
					<h2>Campus Munich</h2>
					<img src="res/muenchen.jpg" alt="Main Campus" id="disabled">
				</div>
				<div class="card" data-name="garching">
					<h2>Campus Garching</h2>
					<img src="res/garching.jpg" alt="Garching Campus">
				</div>
				<div class="card" data-name="heilbronn">
					<h2>Campus Heilbronn</h2>
					<img src="res/heilbronn.jpg" alt="Heilbronn Campus">
				</div>
				<!-- <div class="card" data-name="weihenstephan">
						 <h2>Campus Weihenstephan</h2>
						 <img src="res/weihenstephan.jpg" alt="Weihenstephan Campus" id="disabled">
						 </div> -->
			</div>
			<script src="/js/carousel.js"></script>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h2>Progress and Goals</h2>
			<p>TUM Guessr is a community driven project, you can contribute by signing up and uploading new photos of your own and sharing this site with your friends.</p>
			<label for="photo_goal">Photos: ({{photo_cur}}/{{photo_max}})</label>
			<br>
			<progress id="photo_goal" value="{{photo_cur}}" max="{{photo_max}}"></progress>
			<br>
			<br>
			<label for="user_goal">Users: ({{user_cur}}/{{user_max}})</label>
			<br>
			<progress id="user_goal" value="{{user_cur}}" max="{{user_max}}">{{user_cur}}</progress>
		</div>
  </body>
</html>
